#: ../../../campaigns/t02.wmf/event:163 ../../../campaigns/t02.wmf/event:260
#: ../../../campaigns/t02.wmf/event:272 ../../../campaigns/t02.wmf/event:285
#: ../../../campaigns/t02.wmf/event:297 ../../../campaigns/t02.wmf/event:309
